  <tr bgcolor="#54341C"> 
     <td class="smy" align="right" valign="top">Zone</td> 
     <td><a href="http://www.gameznet.com/cgi-bin/webdata_pro.pl?eqzones.zone_name=Fungus Grove&_layout=Zone&_cgifunction=search">Fungus Grove</a></td> 
   </tr> 
   
  <tr bgcolor="#4A2A12"> 
     <td class="smy" align="right">Description</td> 
     <td> You say, 'Hail, Trep Thilcan' <br />
<br />
Trep Thilcan says 'Hi! You wouldn't be able to do a favor for a poor gnome would you?' <br />
<br />
You say, 'I will do you a favor.' <br />
<br />
Trep Thilcan says 'Well I am trying to setup a shop here, it is such a choice location! I am afraid if I leave though that nasty Halfling over there may steal my spot! She has been watching me keenly all day. I know she is just waiting for me to walk away. If you would go purchase some supplies for me from various locations around the world I would be able to reward you for your time spent. If you are ready to begin?' <br />
<br />
You say, 'I am ready to begin.' <br />
<br />
Trep Thilcan says 'Great! Here is a special crate. It needs to be filled with: <br />
<br />
A purification tablet from Freeport <br />
A keg of beer from Qeynos <br />
A ball of twine from Shadeweaver <br />
A bundle of weapons from Firiona <br />
An armor assortment from Thurgadin <br />
And a case of meat from the Bazaar <br />
<br />
That should give me quite a stock of items to sell to travelers out here.' <br />
<br />
Purification Tablet - Krystin Charcoal or Toxdil in West Freeport<br />
Keg of Beer - Crow in North Qeynos or Darien Felton in Neriak<br />
Ball of Twine - Saren Kaja in Shadeweaver's Thicket <br />
Bundle of Weapons - Dom Pathfinder in Firiona Vie or Ootok in Grobb<br />
Armor Asortment - Terman Underbelly in Thurgadin <br />
Case of Meat - Gaelsori Heriseron in The Bazaar<br />
<br />
Trep Thilcan says 'Fantastic! You got me everything I need to set up shop. Here is some money for your troubles. I hoped you learned something as well. I am sorry I have nothing more to give you except this advice, if you combine: <br />
<br />
A clockwork carapace <br />
A metal rod <br />
Gnomish bolts <br />
Firewater <br />
And Grease <br />
(all found on gnome tinker vendors)<br />
<br />
..in a Toolbox you should get something nice!' <br />
<br />
You gain experience!! <br />
You receive 60 platinum from Trep Thilcan. <br />
<br />
He gives you a Wok recipe. </td> 
   <tr bgcolor="#54341C"> 
     <td class="smy" align="right" valign="top"> Recommended Level </td> 
     <td>None</td> 
